# Enterprise Improvement (Highly Recommended)

Instead of only tag variable:

Use full image variable.

Example:

```text id="3dk8nj"
BASE_RUNTIME_IMAGE=registry.dev.sbiepay.sbi:8443/ubi9/openjdk-21:1.22-1.1749462973
```

Then Dockerfile:

```dockerfile id="3jlwmm"
ARG BASE_RUNTIME_IMAGE

FROM ${BASE_RUNTIME_IMAGE}
```

Advantages:

* easier migration
* supports UBI upgrades
* supports registry migration
* supports JDK family migration
* fewer YAML changes

This becomes very valuable in your SBI centralized GitLab migration program.
